  <name>TkmViewer</name>
  <summary>Visualize TaskMonitor SQLite3 output data</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      TkmViewer provides a good way to visualize output data from TaskMonitor.
    </p>
    <p>Current features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Adaptive UI</li>
      <li>System overview dashboard</li>
      <li>Process and container data</li>
      <li>Other system info data (buddyinfo, diskstats, etc)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
